&lt;ul&gt;
  &lt;li&gt;Remote Admin&lt;/li&gt;
  &lt;li&gt;Support &lt;a href=&quot;http://jekyllrb.com/&quot; title=&quot;Jekyll • Simple, blog-aware, static sites - Transform your plain text into static websites and blogs&quot;&gt;Jekyll&lt;/a&gt; and &lt;a href=&quot;http://gohugo.io/&quot; title=&quot;Hugo :: A fast and modern static website engine&quot;&gt;Hugo&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;

&lt;p&gt;簡單地說，Forestry.io 提供的是 GUI CMS 的服務。&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;Developer 可以輕鬆地用 GitHub + Jekyll 來 Blogging，但，Non-Developer 要用 GitHub + Jekyll 來 Blogging 就不是那麼輕鬆。&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;這之中的癥結在於使用介面，而 Forestry.io 正好補足了 GitHub + Jekyll 相對於 WordPress 所欠缺的部份。&lt;/p&gt;</content><summary type="html">Forestry.io</summary></entry><entry><title type="html">You’re up and running!</title><link href="https://jas9.github.io/9stars//9stars/Hello-World/" rel="alternate" type="text/html" title="You're up and running!" /><published>2016-12-13T00:00:00+00:00</published><updated>2016-12-13T00:00:00+00:00</updated><id>https://jas9.github.io/9stars//9stars/Hello-World</id><content type="html" xml:base="https://jas9.github.io/9stars//9stars/Hello-World/">&lt;p&gt;Strips everything down to the bare minimum, eliminating a lot of complexity.&lt;/p&gt;

